1158
01:21:25,422 --> 01:21:27,934
- Tôi quyết định sẽ bắt đầu...
- Ông ơi!

1159
01:21:28,509 --> 01:21:30,527
- Ông?
- Này con.

1160
01:21:31,262 --> 01:21:33,831
<i>Hey, Baby doll!</i>

1161
01:21:33,931 --> 01:21:36,108
<i>What's going on?</i>

1162
01:21:36,208 --> 01:21:37,485
